    Notebooks[Notebooks<br/>Workbench Images]

    %% External Runtime Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|requires| Python[Python 3.12]
    Notebooks -->|requires| R[R 4.5.1<br/>RStudio only]
    Notebooks -->|requires| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4<br/>Jupyter images]
    Notebooks -->|requires| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x<br/>PyTorch images]
    Notebooks -->|requires| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.16+<br/>TensorFlow images]
    Notebooks -->|requires| CUDA[NVIDIA CUDA 12.8<br/>GPU images]
    Notebooks -->|requires| ROCm[AMD ROCm 6.3/6.4<br/>GPU images]
    Notebooks -->|requires| RStudioServer[RStudio Server 2025.09.0<br/>RStudio images]
    Notebooks -->|requires| CodeServerApp[code-server v4.104.0<br/>CodeServer images]
    Notebooks -->|requires| NodeJS[Node.js 22.18.0<br/>CodeServer]
    Notebooks -->|requires| NGINX[NGINX<br/>RStudio/CodeServer]
    Notebooks -->|requires| Httpd[Apache httpd<br/>RStudio auth]
    Notebooks -->|requires| OpenShiftCLI[oc CLI<br/>stable]

    %% Optional Libraries
    Notebooks -.->|optional| Elyra[Elyra<br/>Pipeline Editor]
    Notebooks -.->|includes| Pandas[Pandas<br/>DataScience]
    Notebooks -.->|includes| NumPy[NumPy<br/>DataScience]
    Notebooks -.->|includes| ScikitLearn[Scikit-learn<br/>DataScience]
    Notebooks -.->|includes| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>TrustyAI images]
    Notebooks -.->|includes| LLMCompressor[LLMCompressor<br/>LLMCompressor images]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|managed by| NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller<br/>Lifecycle management]
    Notebooks -->|displayed in| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI integration]
    Notebooks -->|executed in| KubeflowPipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>Runtime execution]
    Notebooks -.->|integrates| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model versioning]
    Notebooks -.->|integrates| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Pipeline orchestration]

    %% External Services
    Notebooks -->|pulls from| PyPI[PyPI<br/>files.pythonhosted.org<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Notebooks -->|pulls from| CRAN[CRAN<br/>cran.rstudio.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Notebooks -->|connects to| GitHub[GitHub<br/>github.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Notebooks -->|pulls from| Quay[Quay.io<br/>Container registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Notebooks -->|stores data| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Notebooks -->|uses| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Build Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|built by| Konflux[Konflux CI/CD<br/>Build/scan/sign]
    Notebooks -->|base images| UBI9[Red Hat UBI9<br/>Base OS]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|deployed on| OpenShift[OpenShift Platform<br/>Container orchestration]
    Notebooks -->|auth via| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift authentication]

